00:17:44,772 --> 00:17:47,274
Tetapi dia menjadi sangat sulit.

331
00:17:48,025 --> 00:17:50,445
Ruang Rekreasi Gryffindor
Sekolah Sihir Hogwarts

332
00:17:50,528 --> 00:17:53,740
Kebaikan dan kehangatan darimu...

333
